org.jscsi.initiator.connection.phase

Interface IPhase

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FullFeaturePhase, LoginOperationalNegotiationPhase, SecurityNegotiationPhase

    public interface IPhase
    A State Pattern. Each phase of the iSCSI Protocol must implement this interface.
    Author:
    Volker Wildi
